Victor Kwesi Mensah -LRB- born June 6 , 1993 -RRB- , better known by his stage name Vic Mensa , is a Grammy-nominated American rapper from Chicago , Illinois .
He is currently signed to Roc Nation and was a member of the group Kids These Days , which broke up in May 2013 .
He released his first solo mixtape Innanetape .
Mensa is also founder of the hip-hop collective Savemoney which includes frequent collaborator Chance the Rapper .
His debut single `` Down on My Luck '' was released in June 2014 by Virgin EMI .